[ 시나리오 B: PagedAttention 유리 — Wide & Shallow Tree, Budget 제한 (block_size=8) ]
========================================================================
  공유 prefix 없음 → Radix Tree가 루트에서 바로 분기 (wide & shallow)
  block_size=8  /  budget=2 blocks = 16토큰

  req 1:  8토큰  (1 full block + 0 partial)  'Machine learning algorithms learn patterns from labeled datasets'
  req 2:  9토큰  (1 full block + 1 partial)  'Environmental scientists study the effects of climate on life'

  budget 16토큰 기준:
    RadixAttention → 노드(시퀀스 전체) 단위 eviction
                     req1(8tok) + req2(9tok) = 17tok > 16  → 동시 보존 불가, 1개만 유지
    PagedAttention → block(8tok) 단위 eviction
                     req1(1 block) + req2(1 block) = 2 blocks ≤ 2  → 둘 다 보존 가능

  [ 1차 요청 — cold start: MISS → compute → cache에 insert ]
  (캐시가 비어있으므로 모든 요청이 MISS. 하지만 compute 후 cache에 저장됨)

  ▶ req 1 (MISS): 'Machine learning algorithms learn patterns from ' (8tok)
    RadixAttention:  budget 여유 (0+8=8 ≤ 16)
                     → insert req1 완료  |  cache: 8tok  ['Machine learning algorithms learn...'(8tok)]
    PagedAttention:  budget 여유 (0+1=1 ≤ 2)
                     → insert req1 block 완료  |  blocks: 1 blocks  ['Machine learning algorithms learn...'[8tok]]

  ▶ req 2 (MISS): 'Environmental scientists study the effects of cl' (9tok)
    RadixAttention:  budget 초과 (8+9=17 > 16)
                     EVICT 'Machine learning algorithms learn patterns...' (8tok)  ← LRU 노드 통째로 제거
                     → insert req2 완료  |  cache: 9tok  ['Environmental scientists study the...'(9tok)]
    PagedAttention:  budget 여유 (1+1=2 ≤ 2)
                     partial 1tok → 캐시 불가 (block 미달, 버림)
                     → insert req2 block 완료  |  blocks: 2 blocks  ['Machine learning algorithms learn...'[8tok], 'Environmental scientists study the...'[8tok]]

  ── 1차 완료 후 최종 cache 상태 ──
  RadixAttention: 9tok  ['Environmental scientists study the...'(9tok)]
  PagedAttention: 2 blocks  ['Machine learning algorithms learn...'[8tok], 'Environmental scientists study the...'[8tok]]

  RadixAttention: req1(8tok)+req2(9tok)=17tok > budget(16tok)
                  → req2 삽입 시 req1 evict → req2만 생존
  PagedAttention: req1(1 block)+req2(1 block)=2 blocks = budget(2 blocks)
                  → req1·req2 block 둘 다 생존

  ※ 1차 요청은 모두 MISS였지만 compute 후 cache에 삽입됨
     eviction 정책 차이로 살아남은 데이터가 다름 → 2차 HIT 수 차이

  [ 2차 요청 — 동일한 req1·req2 재도착 ]
  (MISS 시에도 compute + insert 수행 — 실제 서빙과 동일)

  ▶ req1 (2차): 'Machine learning algorithms learn patterns from labeled datasets' (8tok)
    RadixAttention: MISS → 8tok 전체 compute → insert
                   budget 초과 (9+8=17 > 16)
                   EVICT 'Environmental scientists study the effects...' (9tok)
                   cache: 8tok  ['Machine learning algorithms learn...'(8tok)]
    PagedAttention: HIT 8tok  → 0tok만 compute → insert (new blocks only)
                   blocks: 2 blocks  ['Environmental scientists study the...'[8tok], 'Machine learning algorithms learn...'[8tok]]

  ▶ req2 (2차): 'Environmental scientists study the effects of climate on life' (9tok)
    RadixAttention: MISS → 9tok 전체 compute → insert
                   budget 초과 (8+9=17 > 16)
                   EVICT 'Machine learning algorithms learn patterns...' (8tok)
                   cache: 9tok  ['Environmental scientists study the...'(9tok)]
    PagedAttention: HIT 8tok  → 1tok만 compute → insert (new blocks only)
                   partial 1tok → 버림
                   blocks: 2 blocks  ['Machine learning algorithms learn...'[8tok], 'Environmental scientists study the...'[8tok]]

